<div class="container col-10">
  <div class="about-me col">
    <div class="col card-photo image w-100 col-12">
      <img src="me.png" alt="" class="image">
    </div>
    <div class="col card card-about w-100 col-12">
      <p>Hi, I'm Neil. A full stack Web Developer from London. I'm a committed learner having spent 6 months of evening and weekends studying and retraining alongside my full time job at the highly regarded Le Wagon bootcamp in London. I'm looking forward to transferring the skills I have learned in my current and previous roles and pairing them with those I've learned over the last few months in an engineering role. </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col card card-links ">
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/neilgoodridge"><i class="fa fab fa-github"></i></a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/neilgoodridge"><i class="fa fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cards-container col-12">
    <div class="cards-holder w-100 col-12">
      <div class="row cards">
        <%= link_to projects_path do %>
        <div class="col card-skills card-projects col-12 w-100" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url(projects.webp)">
          Projects
        </div>
        <% end %>
        <%= link_to skills_path do %>
        <div class="col card-skills card-languages col-12" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url(Skills.png)">
          Skills
        </div>
        <% end %>
        <%= link_to about_path do %>
        <div class="col card-skills" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url(MJ.png)">
          About Me
        </div>
        <% end %>
        <%= link_to contact_path do %>
        <div class="col card-skills" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url(Contact.jpg)">
          Contact Me
        </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
